elkfed.coref.discourse_entities

Class DiscourseEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • elkfed.coref.discourse_entities.DiscourseEntity

  • public class DiscourseEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    A Class that functions as a Discourse Entity where all mentions belonging to the same entity are jointly modeled.

    To be used in entity-centric coreference resolution.

    Author:
    Julian
